8) The "EA-to-EA Packets" That Win

When stakes are high, send packets, not pings.

Scheduling packet example structure:
  - Objective
  - Duration + format
  - Attendees
  - Constraints
  - Options (with TZ)
  - Deadline to confirm
  - Logistics (if in-person)
  - Your contact + escalation channel

Pre-read packet (if needed):
